{"article_id":"MVBwM5HH8Ygvn3x2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Vice President Joe Biden will announce","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that he is running for president","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"next week ,","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"according to multiple reports .","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"The announcement is expected in a video message Wednesday ,","depth":3},{"id":5,"text":"according to three people with knowledge of his plans .","depth":3},{"id":6,"text":"Even though he has not officially launched his campaign","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"Biden has appeared at or near the top of several polls on Democratic candidates .","depth":3},{"id":8,"text":"But not all Democrats would be happy","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"if the former VP ended up their party ' s nominee .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"`` How many of you would like to see Joe Biden get in ?","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Show of hands , ''","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"CNN 's Alisyn Camerota asked the panel of six Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"selected from Ohio , New York , New Jersey and Pennsylvania ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"on `` New Day '' Tuesday morning .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"No one raised their hands .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"`` His time is done , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"said Carol Evans , one of the panelists .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"`` To be honest ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Sen. Biden comes from kind of the good-old-boy politics of the past , ''","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"added another panelist , Russell Banks .","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"Joe Biden represents that new thing","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"that we need , ''","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"a third panelist , Owen Evans , said .","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"`` We need a new economy ,","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"we need new politics","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"and we need someone different . ''","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"( CNN )","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"In addition to the lack of enthusiasm","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"for him entering the race","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"from some Democrats , and his age , Biden has faced recent backlash from several women for inappropriate and unwanted touching .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"\" Social norms have begun to change ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"they ' ve shifted ,","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and the boundaries","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"of protecting personal space","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"have been reset ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"and I get it , \"","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Biden said in a video","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"addressing the claims .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"\" I hear what they ' re saying .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"I understand it .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"I ' ll be much more mindful .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"That ' s my responsibility ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"and I ' ll meet it . \"","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"President Trump predicted earlier this week","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"that the Democratic race would come down to Biden and Sen. Bernie Sanders","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"( I-VT ) .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"\" I believe","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"it will be Crazy Bernie Sanders vs . Sleepy Joe Biden as the two finalists","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"to run against maybe the best Economy in the history of our Country","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"( and MANY other great things ) ! \"","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"he wrote .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"\" I look forward to facing whoever it may be .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"May God Rest Their Soul ! \"","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":109,"left":60,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":60,"left":58,"right":59,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":58,"left":57,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":57,"left":56,"right":2,"relation":"same-unit","nuclear